text:
My friend whom moved there not long ago very dissatisfied with the management and MCST council. Inefficient,  inflexible and unreasonable.
There is little to none community spirit.
High number of tenants.
Rubbish issue, carpark issue, noise issue, security issue etc.
Distance away and unsheltered from public transport.
They regretted their decision moving there.
